             was indicted for <rs id="t18041024-19-off101" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18041024-19-off101" type="offenceCategory" value="deception"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18041024-19-off101" type="offenceSubcategory" value="forgery"></interp>
               feloniously and falsely making and forging a certain order for payment of money
            </rs>, on Messrs. Drummond and Co. for the sum of 13 l. 17 s. 6 d.</p>
               <p>Second Count, for uttering it as true, knowing it to be forged and counterfeited, with intent to defraud 
               
                  <persName id="t18041024-19-victim192" type="victimName">
                     Alexander 
                     Ross
                  <interp inst="t18041024-19-victim192" type="surname" value="Ross"></interp>
